## EXISTING STRUCTURES

There are no existing structures to report.

## ERROR TIPS

### Errors when using extracting but being too far
 -  Make sure to move to the target entity where you want to extract from before extracting items

### Errors when placing into a tile which is occupied by another entity
- Ensure you can place a entity to a tile before attempting placing

### Errors when extracting from a furnace with no ingredients
- Check the furnace status before attempting to extract items. The furnace must have ingredients and have completed processing them to contain the desired output.

### Errors when inventory is full while harvesting
- Check the inventory before attempting to harvest items. If the inventory is full, either craft something or place the items into a chest.
